cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10c9af915eaa0905012707f069dc60b90a4e3ebb","tid":456861,"uid":44814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T10:23:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點解揀呢堆地方</blockquote><br />\n目前無野做 好得閒 隨便安排的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔返日本其他地方？"},{"pid":"fb69f8f2a99fbf99e013b340ad2c381d73e058bc","tid":456861,"uid":8253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T10:42:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點解揀呢堆地方</blockquote><br />\n目前無野做 好得閒 隨便安排的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔返日本其他地方？</blockquote><br />\n我今年入境差唔多滿了<br />\n12月尾仲要去滑雪 要忍下了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51f85c855d6172f7494db640c2efabf97458c683","tid":456861,"uid":5921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T10:43:11.000Z","msg":"有咩地方會去？"},{"pid":"689545d3c4830f35ac5aa04e4f455e573d74b0b5","tid":456861,"uid":44814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T10:48:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點解揀呢堆地方</blockquote><br />\n目前無野做 好得閒 隨便安排的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔返日本其他地方？</blockquote><br />\n我今年入境差唔多滿了<br />\n12月尾仲要去滑雪 要忍下了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n台灣泰國唔啱咩？<br />\n返大陸二線做野住得幾好都好 一諗親食就想屌出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0f23430225d0ad2a3b1b1536071317e0088977a","tid":456861,"uid":8253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T10:49:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有咩地方會去？</blockquote><br />\n唔知 我無研究景點<br />\n但去麗江個時會上玉龍雪山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無巴打可以講下包車 我係麗江住悅榕莊"},{"pid":"2fa55ca0a738cb6995d731ed9c5f55c078bb6e4c","tid":456861,"uid":8253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T10:50:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點解揀呢堆地方</blockquote><br />\n目前無野做 好得閒 隨便安排的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔返日本其他地方？</blockquote><br />\n我今年入境差唔多滿了<br />\n12月尾仲要去滑雪 要忍下了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n台灣泰國唔啱咩？<br />\n返大陸二線做野住得幾好都好 一諗親食就想屌出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n全撚部都係油 辣 真係不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n台灣去到悶 泰國未去過 有機會去下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f792c623f22d93272f1b0ff2a498be10618b540","tid":456861,"uid":71712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T10:51:39.000Z","msg":"可以去下束河果邊<br />\n雪山來講肉龍都算呃錢"},{"pid":"c20110e161896f6e3261b8bcd1161a8fd2db5b2e","tid":456861,"uid":152963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T10:56:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可以去下束河果邊<br />\n雪山來講肉龍都算呃錢</blockquote><br />\n大概幾錢人仔啊"},{"pid":"c943b81be5698c632fe3013103f767955e368c9a","tid":456861,"uid":8253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T11:12:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>可以去下束河果邊<br />\n雪山來講肉龍都算呃錢</blockquote><br />\n大概幾錢人仔啊</blockquote><br />\n酒店係束河古鎮附近<br />\n點解玉龍呃錢？我全程最期待呢個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03dcb56aaaa5800afc6e2dbf3cf38e85ba32f7fa","tid":456861,"uid":106032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T13:30:17.000Z","msg":"坐高鐵去?"},{"pid":"e0241ad23ed32c94e3ad2f29a59c7d8471074ad1","tid":456861,"uid":8253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T14:16:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>坐高鐵去?</blockquote><br />\n全程坐飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f877f556ef8ccdbcd5c117219ef514db806e96e","tid":456861,"uid":5921,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T15:56:26.000Z","msg":"留名睇玉龍 睇吓有無伏先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5238937f2db56c1886384173b31ec9ba715db261","tid":456861,"uid":134711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T16:21:32.000Z","msg":"點解要去南昌？"},{"pid":"6864713755b970140da16034968af8bec3d6397f","tid":456861,"uid":8253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T16:23:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解要去南昌？</blockquote><br />\n屋企係附近有生意 去南昌係臨時決定 真係無野玩 後日去下廬山都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f4b24079ea21f729db68ddebe6783a233e2b146","tid":456861,"uid":134711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T16:43:59.000Z","msg":"I see"},{"pid":"c534fcf0c2035f57ccb7280667a9370732a74900","tid":456861,"uid":49626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T04:54:25.000Z","msg":"岩岩玉龍返黎 500人仔包票 車 氧氣 水 大嬲 <br />\n包中午一餐 再加去個湖到睇 真係幾撚靚 <br />\n但上到頂真係差d暈撚左 第一次去咁高真係有高山症"}]}